23
00:00:51.897 --> 00:00:52.829
THE HEAD CHEERLEADER,

24
00:00:52.865 --> 00:00:54.831
AND AN AWARD-WINNING
PIANIST.


25
00:00:54.867 --> 00:00:57.034
