BY JOURNEY BEGINS TO PLAY]


27
00:00:58.237 --> 00:01:00.170
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
BOYS AND GIRLS,


28
00:01:00.305 --> 00:01:01.838
ANY PANTHER PRESENT,

29
00:01:01.907 --> 00:01:03.240
PLEASE RISE TO YOUR FEET

30
00:01:03.375 --> 00:01:05.241
AND GIVE A WARM,
LOVING WELCOME


31
00:01:05.277 --> 00:01:06.309
TO OUR PROM ROYALTY...

32
00:01:06.345 --> 00:01:07.978
READY?

33
00:01:08.047 --> 00:01:09.312
[GIGGLING]

34
00:01:09.315 --> 00:01:10.914
JOHN PATTON
AND KATHY BLAIR!


35
00:01:10.983 --> 00:01:13.250
[CROWD CHEERING]

36
00:01:13.385 --> 00:01:16.119
[♪♪]

37
00:01:42.748 --> 00:01:45.482
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

38
00:01:45.484 --> 00:01:47.317
OUR PROM KING
AND QUEEN!


39
00:01:55.060 --> 00:01:56.293
AND NOW,

40
00:01:56.295 --> 00:01:59.295
THE PROM KING AND QUEEN
WILL TAKE THEIR FIRST DANCE.


41
00:01:59.331 --> 00:02:00.496
PLEASE.

42
00:02:00.532 --> 00:02:02.366
[CHEERING AND APPLAUSE]

43
