IN A SMOKY ROOM ♪

44
00:02:10.943 --> 00:02:14.978
♪ THE SMELL OF WINE
AND CHEAP PERFUME ♪


45
00:02:15.047 --> 00:02:18.381
♪ FOR A SMILE
