1455
01:11:47.615 --> 01:11:48.447
MR. PATTON!

1456
01:11:49.617 --> 01:11:50.616
YES, SIR?

1457
01:11:50.685 --> 01:11:53.486
IS IT POSSIBLE THAT YOU ARE..

1458
01:11:53.621 --> 01:11:54.654
SINGING?

1459
01:11:56.024 --> 01:11:57.890
