1463
01:12:05.834 --> 01:12:07.366
"THE WHEELS ON THE BUS," SIR.

1464
01:12:07.501 --> 01:12:09.368
[BABY FUSSING]

1465
01:12:09.503 --> 01:12:10.570
UP, PLEASE.

1466
01:12:12.373 --> 01:12:13.906
PENS DOWN AND STAND.

1467
01:12:14.041 --> 01:12:15.007
NOW.

1468
01:12:16.511 --> 01:12:18.711
"THE WHEELS ON THE BUS."

1469
01:12:18.846 --> 01:12:21.313
SO THAT MR. PATTON'S
INEXPLICABLY PRESENT SON


1470
01:12:21.382 --> 01:12:23.649
MIGHT SLEEP.

