♪ THE HORN ON THE BUS
GOES BEEP, BEEP, BEEP ♪


1482
01:12:58.486 --> 01:13:03.389
♪ ALL DAY LONG ♪

1483
01:13:13.101 --> 01:13:15.100
PROFESSOR KOWAL
JUST GAVE ME


1484
01:13:15.169 --> 01:13:16.768
ANOTHER HUGE GIFT.

1485
01:13:16.804 --> 01:13:18.904
IF I PASS THE FINAL,
I PASS THE COURSE,


1486
01:13:18.940 --> 01:13:20.106
KEEP MY SCHOLARSHIP.

1487
01:13:20.241 --> 01:13:21.440
AND YOU WILL.

1488
01:13:21.575 --> 01:13:23.042
I'M NOT SO SURE.

1489
01:13:24.412 --> 01:13:26.579
I HAVE TO BE REALISTIC,
YOU KNOW?


1490
01:13:26.581 --> 01:13:28.915
CALC. HAS KNOCKED ME AROUND
PRETTY GOOD.


1491
01:13:29.050 --> 01:13:30.182
MAYBE IT'S TIME
I CALLED THE FIGHT.


1492
01:13:30.251 --> 01:13:31.717
OH, DON'T TALK NONSENSE, JOHN.

1493
01:13:31.753 --> 01:13:32.785
YOU'RE A HARVARD MAN.

1494
01:13:32.920 --> 01:13:33.853
YOU BELONG THERE.

1495
01:13:33.988 --> 01:13:35.922
[CHUCKLES]
THAT MAKES THREE OF YOU.


1496
01:13:37.591 --> 01:13:41.260
YOU, KATHY, AND MY MOM,
YOU ALL SAY I BELONG AT HARVARD.


1497
01:13:41.329 --> 01:13:43.595
BUT YOU KNOW WHO DOESN'T?

1498
01:13:43.631 --> 01:13:44.597
HARVARD.

1499
01:13:44.599 --> 01:13:46.131
I MEAN, PEOPLE
LIKE KOWAL


1500
01:13:46.167 --> 01:13:47.199
MAKE ALLOWANCES FOR ME,

1501
01:13:47.335 --> 01:13:48.801
BUT THEY NEVER SAY
I BELONG THERE...


1502
01:13:50.805 --> 01:13:53.205
AND MAYBE I DON'T.

1503
01:13:53.341 --> 01:13:55.541
COME WITH ME, JOHN.

1504
01:13:55.543 --> 01:13:56.742
I WANT TO SHOW YOU SOMETHING.

1505
01:13:56.744 --> 01:13:58.678
I'VE GOT TO CHANGE ADAM.

1506
01:13:58.813 --> 01:13:59.812
IT'S IMPORTANT.

1507
01:13:59.881 --> 01:14:01.247
DON'T MAKE ME
PUT A CURSE ON YOU.


1508
01:14:02.617 --> 01:14:03.816
OKAY.

1509
01:14:03.818 --> 01:14:07.352
NOW, LOOK.
LOOK THERE.


1510
01:14:07.388 --> 01:14:09.221
YOU SEE THOSE LILACS?

1511
01:14:09.257 --> 01:14:11.290
NOW, I'VE BEEN LIVING HERE
FOR 35 YEARS,


1512
01:14:11.292 --> 01:14:13.025
AND EVERY SPRING,

1513
01:14:13.027 --> 01:14:16.629
THESE SAME LILACS GROW
IN THIS SAME SPOT.


1514
01:14:16.631 --> 01:14:17.763
NOW, NOBODY EVER
TENDS IT, WATERS IT,


1515
01:14:17.799 --> 01:14:19.431
FEEDS IT,

1516
01:14:19.500 --> 01:14:20.699
OR ENCOURAGES IT
IN ANY WAY,


1517
01:14:20.735 --> 01:14:21.967
AND EVERY YEAR,

1518
01:14:21.970 --> 01:14:26.972
STILL IT FIGHTS THE ODDS
AND FINDS THE LIGHT, AND...


1519
01:14:27.008 --> 01:14:28.907
BLOOMS,

1520
01:14:28.977 --> 01:14:32.511
AND THAT IS EXACTLY
WHAT YOU ARE GOING TO DO,


1521
01:14:32.513 --> 01:14:35.514
BECAUSE YOU ARE A SURVIVOR.

1522
01:14:37.785 --> 01:14:39.051
THE CARDS TELL YOU THAT?

1523
01:14:39.053 --> 01:14:42.355
MY HEART TELLS ME THAT.

1524
01:14:44.392 --> 01:14:45.458
NOW, GIVE ME THAT BABY BOY.

1525
01:14:45.460 --> 01:14:47.226
YOU'VE BEEN HOGGING HIM
ALL MORNING.


1526
01:14:48.229 --> 01:14:50.329
NOW, YOU--

1527
01:14:50.464 --> 01:14:52.865
YOU LISTEN TO ME.

1528
01:14:53.000 --> 01:14:54.866
YOU'VE GOT TO
FACE FACTS.


1529
01:14:54.902 --> 01:14:56.135
YOU'VE GOT
TWO MOTHERS NOW,


1530
01:14:56.137 --> 01:14:57.669
WHETHER YOU LIKE IT
OR NOT,


1531
01:14:57.705 --> 01:14:58.738
AND I BELIEVE IN YOU

1532
01:14:58.873 --> 01:15:01.406
JUST AS MUCH
AS THE OTHER ONE DOES.


1533
01:15:01.442 --> 01:15:02.541
NOW, LET'S GO IN.

1534
01:15:02.610 --> 01:15:04.476
YOU'VE GOT
HOMEWORK TO DO,


1535
01:15:04.512 --> 01:15:08.047
AND I'VE GOT
SOUP TO MAKE.


1536
01:15:12.086 --> 01:15:13.552
[BABY CRYING]

1537
01:15:13.588 --> 01:15:15.054
SHH, SHH...

1538
01:15:15.189 --> 01:15:16.688
IT'S OKAY, BUD.

1539
01:15:16.758 --> 01:15:18.023
IT'S OKAY...

1540
01:15:18.092 --> 01:15:20.893
SHH...

1541
01:15:21.028 --> 01:15:22.094
FLORENCE
THE NEIGHBOR'S


1542
01:15:22.229 --> 01:15:23.362
BRINGING
THE BABY DROPS.


1543
01:15:23.431 --> 01:15:24.630
DID YOU TAKE
HIS TEMP AGAIN?


1544
01:15:24.765 --> 01:15:26.432
YEAH, HE'S
STILL RISING.


1545
01:15:26.501 --> 01:15:27.633
IT'LL BE OKAY.

1546
01:15:27.702 --> 01:15:29.434
[BABY CRYING]

1547
01:15:29.470 --> 01:15:30.902
DO YOU HAVE CLASS THIS MORNING?

1548
01:15:30.938 --> 01:15:32.838
YEAH, CALC. IN TWO HOURS.

1549
01:15:32.840 --> 01:15:35.040
I'LL MAKE SOME COFFEE.

1550
01:15:35.076 --> 01:15:38.744
[BABY CRYING]

1551
01:15:41.616 --> 01:15:44.516
HE'S FINALLY CONKED OUT.

1552
01:15:44.552 --> 01:15:45.985
HOPEFULLY HE'LL SLEEP
FOR A WHILE.


1553
01:15:46.120 --> 01:15:47.920
SIT DOWN, EAT.

1554
01:15:47.922 --> 01:15:50.222
NO, COFFEE'LL DO.

1555
01:15:51.225 --> 01:15:53.025
COULDN'T YOU CUT CLASS
JUST THIS ONCE?


1556
01:15:54.862 --> 01:15:56.394
CAN'T, IT'S THE REVIEW
FOR THE FINAL.


1557
01:15:56.431 --> 01:15:59.198
WELL, YOU NEED
SOMETHING TO EAT.


1558
01:15:59.333 --> 01:16:00.533
YOU NEED SOMETHING
IN YOUR STOMACH.


1559
01:16:00.668 --> 01:16:02.601
YOU'VE GOT TO HAVE FUEL.

1560
01:16:02.670 --> 01:16:04.403
SIT DOWN.

1561
01:16:07.475 --> 01:16:08.974
[VOICE BREAKING]:
SHE STOPPED CALLING, DOROTHY.


1562
01:16:10.811 --> 01:16:12.711
I LEFT HER THREE MESSAGES
AND SHE HASN'T CALLED BACK.


1563
01:16:14.682 --> 01:16:16.281
WELL...

1564
01:16:16.317 --> 01:16:17.483
SHE'S FEELING GUILTY.

1565
01:16:17.618 --> 01:16:19.885
SHE'S ASHAMED

1566
01:16:20.020 --> 01:16:22.020
AND UPSET.

1567
01:16:22.056 --> 01:16:23.222
IT'S HER, NOT YOU.

1568
01:16:29.363 --> 01:16:30.496
I GOT TO GO.

1569
01:16:30.565 --> 01:16:32.364
JOHN..

1570
01:16:32.433 --> 01:16:33.832
IT'S OKAY, I'M FINE.

1571
01:16:33.901 --> 01:16:35.834
I'M HOME ALL DAY.

1572
01:16:35.903 --> 01:16:37.002
DON'T
-DON'T WORRY.

1573
01:16:38.706 --> 01:16:39.972
THANKS, MOM.

1574
01:16:39.974 --> 01:16:41.106
WE OWE YOU ONE.

1575
01:16:41.142 --> 01:16:44.510
[SNIFFLING]

1576
01:16:44.512 --> 01:16:46.612
JOHN...

1577
01:16:52.787 --> 01:16:56.088
[SOBBING]

1578
01:16:57.425 --> 01:16:59.458
DON'T WORRY.

1579
01:16:59.527 --> 01:17:00.659
DON'T WORRY...

1580
01:17:00.661 --> 01:17:04.697
IT'S GOING TO
BE ALL RIGHT.


1581
01:17:05.800 --> 01:17:08.200
TAKE ONE
AND PASS THEM BACK.


1582
01:17:08.335 --> 01:17:10.536
THIS IS NOT JUST
A STUDY GUIDE.


1583
01:17:10.605 --> 01:17:12.938
THIS IS YOUR NEW
BEST FRIEND.


1584
01:17:12.940 --> 01:17:15.874
TREAT IT
WITH RESPECT,


1585
01:17:15.943 --> 01:17:17.143
AND IT'LL PAY YOU BACK
ON FINALS DAY.


1586
01:17:28.355 --> 01:17:31.090
UNFORTUNATELY, THERE ISN'T
A PRESCRIPTION FOR THIS.


1587
01:17:31.092 --> 01:17:33.492
A VIRUS HAS TO
RUN ITS COURSE.


1588
01:17:33.561 --> 01:17:35.828
WELL, IT'S BEEN
A FEW DAYS ALREADY.


1589
01:17:35.963 --> 01:17:38.096
IT'S MUCH WORSE
AT NIGHT.


1590
01:17:38.132 --> 01:17:40.566
HIS SLEEP,
IT'S SO RAGGED.


1591
01:17:40.568 --> 01:17:41.633
GET SOME
ELECTROLYTES.


1592
01:17:41.702 --> 01:17:43.302
THEY ARE CRUCIAL
WITH A VIRUS.


1593
01:17:43.437 --> 01:17:45.837
FEVER DEHYDRATES
A BABY FAST.


1594
01:17:45.873 --> 01:17:47.573
USE A BOTTLE.

1595
01:17:47.708 --> 01:17:50.576
HE'LL TAKE IT
EASIER THAT WAY.


1596
01:17:50.645 --> 01:17:51.710
THANK YOU.

1597
01:17:51.845 --> 01:17:53.312
AND LOOK AFTER
YOURSELF.


1598
01:17:53.447 --> 01:17:56.315
YOU'RE NO GOOD TO ADAM
IF YOU GO DOWN, TOO.


1599
01:17:56.317 --> 01:17:57.849
YOU GOT ANYONE
TO SPELL YOU?


1600
01:17:57.885 --> 01:17:58.984
NO.

1601
01:17:58.986 --> 01:18:02.922
NO, OUR LANDLADY'S
AWAY FOR A FEW DAYS.


1602
01:18:03.057 --> 01:18:04.256
[BABY CRYING]

1603
01:18:04.292 --> 01:18:05.391
WE'LL BE FINE.

1604
01:18:05.393 --> 01:18:06.792
WE'LL BE FINE...

1605
01:18:06.927 --> 01:18:08.794
THANK YOU, DOCTOR.

1606
01:18:08.929 --> 01:18:10.729
THANK YOU.

1607
01:18:12.266 --> 01:18:15.267
[RAIN POURING, 
THUNDER BOOMS]

1608
01:18:15.336 --> 01:18:18.504
[CRYING INCONSOLABLY]

1609
01:18:26.714 --> 01:18:28.614
HEY, BUD.

1610
01:18:28.616 --> 01:18:29.881
HEY.

1611
01:18:29.917 --> 01:18:31.416
HEY...

1612
01:18:31.485 --> 01:18:33.252
OH, MY GOD.

1613
01:18:39.560 --> 01:18:41.160
HOLD ON, BUDDY, IT'S ALL RIGHT!

1614
01:18:41.162 --> 01:18:43.829
HANG ON, ADAM,
JUST A COUPLE MORE MINUTES.


1615
01:18:43.898 --> 01:18:45.231
DADDY'S GOING TO
MAKE IT ALL BETTER, OKAY?


1616
01:18:45.366 --> 01:18:46.365
I PROMISE.

1617
01:18:47.268 --> 01:18:48.300
NO!

1618
01:18:49.036 --> 01:18:50.135
OH, FOR...

1619
01:18:52.306 --> 01:18:54.373
[SHOUTS IN FRUSTRATION]

1620
01:18:55.443 --> 01:18:58.310
[BABY CRYING]

1621
01:19:01.315 --> 01:19:05.150
[THUNDER CRASHES, RAIN POURS]

1622
01:19:11.058 --> 01:19:13.692
[BABY WAILING]

1623
01:19:28.876 --> 01:19:30.309
I GOT YOU.
IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT.


1624
01:19:35.683 --> 01:19:36.982
THAT'S IT.

1625
01:19:37.985 --> 01:19:40.018
HEY, HANG ON,
BUDDY.


1626
01:19:40.087 --> 01:19:41.220
[BABY CRYING]

1627
01:19:41.222 --> 01:19:42.220
IT'S ALL RIGHT, ADAM.

1628
01:19:42.256 --> 01:19:44.223
DADDY'S GOING TO MAKE
YOU FEEL ALL BETTER.


1629
01:19:44.358 --> 01:19:45.391
I GOT YOUR BACK, REMEMBER?

1630
01:19:46.794 --> 01:19:47.759
OKAY?

1631
01:19:47.828 --> 01:19:50.095
HANG IN THERE.

1632
01:19:50.230 --> 01:19:51.630
THANK YOU.

1633
01:19:54.802 --> 01:19:55.934
THANK YOU.

1634
01:20:01.042 --> 01:20:03.642
HELLO!

1635
01:20:03.644 --> 01:20:05.878
I'M BACK!

1636
01:20:09.183 --> 01:20:10.349
[BABY CRYING]

1637
01:20:15.856 --> 01:20:17.489
SHH, SHH, SHH...

1638
01:20:26.334 --> 01:20:28.534
SHH, SHH, SHH, SHH...

1639
01:20:30.971 --> 01:20:32.137
[BABY FUSSING]

1640
01:20:32.173 --> 01:20:33.271
SHH, SHH...

1641
01:20:33.341 --> 01:20:34.272
[WHISPERING]:
GET YOU A BOTTLE?


1642
01:20:34.308 --> 01:20:35.407
COME ON, YEAH.

1643
01:20:35.476 --> 01:20:37.543
LET'S GET YOU A BOTTLE.

1644
01:21:06.774 --> 01:21:08.607
EXCUSE ME.

1645
01:21:15.716 --> 01:21:17.316
I WANT TO THANK YOU

1646
01:21:17.318 --> 01:21:19.451
FOR YOUR INCREDIBLE
GENEROSITY


1647
01:21:19.453 --> 01:21:21.453
AND SUPPORT THIS YEAR.

1648
01:21:21.522 --> 01:21:23.254
I WISH I COULD HAVE
REPAID YOU


1649
01:21:23.290 --> 01:21:24.523
WITH A PASSING GRADE.

1650
01:21:24.525 --> 01:21:27.760
IT'S ONLY 3:30.
YOU'RE NOT OUT OF TIME, JOHN.


1651
01:21:29.663 --> 01:21:32.197
I'M SORRY, SIR, BUT...

1652
01:21:32.332 --> 01:21:33.399
I AM.

1653
01:21:39.940 --> 01:21:44.209
THESE FLASHY NEW DUDS
ARE FROM YOUR GRANDMOTHER


1654
01:21:44.344 --> 01:21:45.610
WHO LOVES YOU VERY MUCH

1655
01:21:45.679 --> 01:21:47.479
AND CAN HARDLY WAIT TO SEE YOU,

1656
01:21:47.548 --> 01:21:49.948
JUST LIKE EVERYONE ELSE
IN BOISE.


1657
01:21:50.083 --> 01:21:51.283
[TELEPHONE RINGS]

1658
01:21:52.620 --> 01:21:54.486
YOU'RE GOING TO
LOVE IT THERE, ADAM.


1659
01:21:54.522 --> 01:21:57.288
THE SKIES ARE BLUE AND BOLD,

1660
01:21:57.324 --> 01:22:00.091
AND THE MOUNTAINS GO ON FOREVER.

1661
01:22:00.127 --> 01:22:01.693
IT'S A WONDERFUL,
WONDERFUL PLACE.


1662
01:22:01.829 --> 01:22:04.630
JOHN!

1663
01:22:04.765 --> 01:22:05.831
JOHN, DO YOU HEAR THAT?

1664
01:22:08.235 --> 01:22:10.502
I BELIEVE THAT'S DEAN FROST
CALLING AGAIN.


1665
01:22:10.538 --> 01:22:11.637
YOU KNOW
SOMETHING ELSE


1666
01:22:11.639 --> 01:22:13.238
GREAT ABOUT BOISE?

1667
01:22:13.240 --> 01:22:14.840
NO WICKED WITCHES.

1668
01:22:14.842 --> 01:22:17.308
WE STOP THEM AT THE BORDER,
AND WE BURN THEIR POINTY HATS.


1669
01:22:17.344 --> 01:22:18.911
AND IS THIS IS
HOW YOU'LL TEACH HIM


1670
01:22:19.046 --> 01:22:20.445
TO DEAL WITH DIFFICULT PEOPLE?

1671
01:22:20.448 --> 01:22:22.247
OUR AUNT DOROTHY.

1672
01:22:22.382 --> 01:22:23.448
WE'LL MISS HER, WON'T WE?

1673
01:22:23.484 --> 01:22:24.516
[BABY CRYING]

1674
01:22:24.552 --> 01:22:25.583
AW...

1675
01:22:25.619 --> 01:22:29.588
THAT VOICE OF LOGIC AND REASON.

1676
01:22:29.723 --> 01:22:31.990
LISTEN, IF I
COME BACK A TOAD,


1677
01:22:32.125 --> 01:22:34.827
IT'S ON YOUR HEAD.

1678
01:22:37.465 --> 01:22:40.766
[GIGGLING AND COOING TO BABY]

1679
01:22:51.879 --> 01:22:53.612
[SIGHS HAPPILY]

1680
01:22:53.747 --> 01:22:54.680
I'VE ALREADY TURNED IN
MY STUDENT I.D.


1681
01:22:54.815 --> 01:22:55.747
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU'RE AFTER.

1682
01:22:55.883 --> 01:22:57.282
YOU'RE HEADING HOME, JOHN?

1683
01:22:57.351 --> 01:22:58.950
FAST AS I CAN GET THERE.

1684
01:22:58.986 --> 01:23:01.085
TOMORROW MORNING,

1685
01:23:01.121 --> 01:23:02.287
FIRST STAGECOACH OUT.

1686
01:23:02.422 --> 01:23:03.956
STAGECOACH?

1687
01:23:03.958 --> 01:23:05.824
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
INTO BOISE, MA'AM.


1688
01:23:05.826 --> 01:23:07.292
THEM FANCY PLANES,

1689
01:23:07.361 --> 01:23:09.427
THEY DON'T BOTHER MUCH
WITH OUR LITTLE COW TOWN.


1690
01:23:09.497 --> 01:23:11.129
YOU THINK I'M A SNOB, JOHN?

1691
01:23:14.502 --> 01:23:16.834
NO, MA'AM, A COWARD.

1692
01:23:16.871 --> 01:23:20.505
YOUR IVORY TOWER
HAS NO WINDOWS IN IT.


1693
01:23:20.508 --> 01:23:23.442
YOU JUDGE WHAT YOU CAN'T SEE

1694
01:23:23.444 --> 01:23:24.710
BECAUSE YOU'RE TOO AFRAID
TO LOOK,


1695
01:23:24.845 --> 01:23:27.512
AND YOU THINK LIFE CAN BE
LIVED BY A TEXTBOOK,


1696
01:23:27.548 --> 01:23:30.181
BUT IT CAN'T.

1697
01:23:30.217 --> 01:23:31.984
WE'RE JUST ALONG FOR THE RIDE.

1698
01:23:33.854 --> 01:23:35.587
A BUMPY ONE.

1699
01:23:35.656 --> 01:23:37.789
ABSOLUTELY,

1700
01:23:37.925 --> 01:23:40.325
BUT A ROCKY ROAD CAN LEAD
TO A SPECTACULAR BEACH.


1701
01:23:40.460 --> 01:23:43.996
OR A DRUGSTORE.

1702
01:23:46.100 --> 01:23:47.099
PLEASE.

1703
01:23:49.003 --> 01:23:51.103
OH, COME ON, JOHN, PLEASE.

1704
01:23:56.110 --> 01:23:57.809
LAST WEEK I SAW YOU
IN THE DRUGSTORE


1705
01:23:57.945 --> 01:23:59.010
WITH YOUR LITTLE BOY

1706
01:23:59.046 --> 01:24:00.211
WHEN YOU WERE BUYING MEDICINE,

1707
01:24:00.247 --> 01:24:03.081
AND IT CHANGED

1708
01:24:03.083 --> 01:24:06.084
EVERYTHING I FELT ABOUT YOU.

1709
01:24:06.120 --> 01:24:07.151
WATCHING THE WAY

1710
01:24:07.187 --> 01:24:09.220
YOU SHIELDED HIM
FROM THE LIGHTS,


1711
01:24:09.290 --> 01:24:11.189
SEEING THE WAY
YOU CRADLED HIM...


1712
01:24:13.193 --> 01:24:14.559
I REALIZED

1713
01:24:14.628 --> 01:24:17.262
THAT I WAS WRONG TO JUDGE YOU.

1714
01:24:19.600 --> 01:24:22.167
YOU'RE A GOOD FATHER, JOHN.

1715
01:24:22.169 --> 01:24:25.537
I SAW IT A HUNDRED
DIFFERENT WAYS THAT NIGHT.


1716
01:24:28.508 --> 01:24:30.208
I SAW HOW DEEPLY
YOU LOVE YOUR SON.


1717
01:24:33.514 --> 01:24:35.180
SO WHEN WORD CAME

1718
01:24:35.315 --> 01:24:37.715
THAT YOU'D FAILED
YOUR CALCULUS FINAL,


1719
01:24:37.751 --> 01:24:38.984
I WASN'T SURPRISED.

1720
01:24:38.986 --> 01:24:42.654
I KNEW IMMEDIATELY
WHAT HAD HAPPENED.


1721
01:24:42.789 --> 01:24:44.256
YOU CHOSE
TAKING CARE OF YOUR SON


1722
01:24:44.391 --> 01:24:46.658
OVER STUDYING FOR YOUR EXAM.

1723
01:24:48.528 --> 01:24:52.731
THERE'S A CERTAIN HONOR
IN THAT F,


1724
01:24:52.800 --> 01:24:55.400
BECAUSE IT MEANT THAT
YOU'D DONE THE RIGHT THING.


1725
01:24:57.738 --> 01:24:59.271
YOU PUT YOUR CHILD FIRST.

1726
01:25:01.642 --> 01:25:04.676
I'VE ADDED A STIPEND

1727
01:25:04.712 --> 01:25:06.478
FOR CHILDCARE,

1728
01:25:06.480 --> 01:25:10.415
AND A GUARANTEE
OF CAMPUS HOUSING.


1729
01:25:10.550 --> 01:25:12.284
THE REST OF THE SCHOLARSHIP
WILL REMAIN THE SAME


1730
01:25:12.419 --> 01:25:15.487
WITH A LITTLE MORE FLEXIBILITY
IN GRADE EXPECTATION.


1731
01:25:17.958 --> 01:25:20.158
AN HONORABLE MAN DESERVES
A SECOND CHANCE, JOHN,


1732
01:25:20.194 --> 01:25:22.494
AND HARVARD'S
GIVING YOU ONE.


1733
01:25:22.496 --> 01:25:26.098
WE DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO HANG ONTO THE GOOD GUYS.


1734
01:25:29.436 --> 01:25:32.304
WELCOME BACK, JOHN PATTON.

